  "detailed_description": "<h1>PLAY THE FULL VERSION</h1><p></p><br><h1>CHECK OUT TOY TINKER SIMULATOR</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428610/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1658935778\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428610/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1658935778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428610/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1658935778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Animal Rescuer: Prologue is a free standalone version of the game Animal Rescuer, featuring the initial part of the story. Our hero is helping lovely animals through exploring an epic world with faster gameplay and increased quest and combat intensity.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Engage in a great roleplaying experience – achieve quests and complete objectives of the entire story</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Acquire plants to prepare medicine for lovely animals needing help</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Meet new people along the way through fantastic cities and villages of this world</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Demonstrate warrior abilities in epic combats with enemies and bosses</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428610/extras/9ca3d4771e2be0e6f6ae9ed724bb9f92.poster.avif?t=1658935778\" width=730 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428610/extras/9ca3d4771e2be0e6f6ae9ed724bb9f92.webm?t=1658935778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428610/extras/9ca3d4771e2be0e6f6ae9ed724bb9f92.mp4?t=1658935778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428610/extras/2223096e2d1af7023a8becb484e44080.avif?t=1658935778\" width=480 height=870 /></span>",
